name: Alvis
description:
This is Alvis.
Alvis' birth name was Charles.
Alvis loves Elvis Presley.
Charles dreamt of being an Elvis impersonator.
Charles legally changed his name to Elvis.
Charles should have double checked for typos on his name change application.
